<section class="work" id="bcm">
	<h2 class="project_title central" > Baptist Community Ministries Foundation - SEEK System</h2>
	<p class="blurb central"><a href="bcm.org" target="_blank">Baptist Community Ministries Foundation</a>, a medium-sized New Orleans based private foundation, asked me to help them build a system for digitally tracking, reporting on, and evaluating their grantmaking portfolio.  In addition to project managing the development of the internal SEEK software at the heart of that effort, I was deeply involved in redesigning the information gathering and reporting processes for the organization - helping make sure they asked the right questions from the beginning.  The system is currently used to help make data-driven decisions regarding what elements of their grant-making portfolio will be focused on in the future, in addition to helping smooth out their complex day-to-day grant management. </p>
