<section class="work" id="rsd">
	<h2 class="project_title central" > <a target="_blank" href="http://rsdla.net"> Recovery School District:</a> Pathways Instructor Evaluation</h2>
	<p class="blurb central">The Recovery School District, a unique school district created to help failing schools in Louisiana, introduced a centralized system for teacher evaluation and feedback in 2010 - RSD Pathways.  Implementing this system among dozens of schools, and developing tools for understanding the results was a massive challenge.  As a consultant for the district, I had two primary roles.  First, I developed training materials to introduce the data entry system to teachers and principals, and led trainings in which it was used.   Second, I created a simple, flexible system that teachers, principals, and administrators could use for weekly analysis of evaluation data.  The system pulled out key indicators of performance and highlighted reporting issues, using Visual Basic and Excel. </p>
